parameters: \n<Momo>Good evening~!
\n<Hat Man>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F] Whoa!? W-What is it?!

\n<Momo>Alright, here we go~! It's time for the Yuva Guns
\I[12]!

\n<Momo>Both of you, say it according to the meeting plan,
okay?!
\n<Sawa>I'm sorry... I hesitated \r[ at the last minute...
\n<Kino>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[FF] Hmm... Ah, sorry.

\n<Brown-haired man>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F] What the hell are you guys
doing, just barging in----... Oh? Oh my?

The brown-haired man's expression softened as soon
as he saw Kino.

\n<Brown-haired man>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F] Kino-chan~♪ What's up? Are you
here to \r[reward and encourage] me again?

\n<Hat Man>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F] Huh? Could it be, from the
other day?

\n<Brown-haired man>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F] Hey, Udo-san brought a girl
for us to share. We're gonna have a threesome all
night long (laughs).

\n<Hat Man>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F] Damn, it's always when I'm not
around... And she's pretty cute too... Huh? I feel
like I've seen her somewhere before...

\n<Sawa>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[FF] Kino... Could it be that you
were familiar with this place...?

\n<Kino>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[FF] Ah... Please keep this a
secret from those two. This is the condition for
me helping out.
\n<Momo>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[FF] Kino-chan...

\n<Brown-haired man>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F] What... Could it be, today
you'll be with the three of us?

\n<Kino>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[FF] That's right~☆ I couldn't
forget about you guys~ I came back again♪ I
couldn't forget about you guys~ I came back again♪

\n<Hat Man>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F] Shaa! Kino-chan is mine to
use, you know! She's totally my type♪

\n<Momo>Well then... Momo wants big brother to do it with
her~ \I[12]

\n<Brown-haired man>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F] Hey, great♪ How about bringing
that girl along too?

\n<Hat Man>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F] Huh? You've had your fun
plenty! Leave this one to me!

\n<Brown-haired man>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F] Who cares! It's your fault for
not being here!

\n<Sawa>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[FF] Then, then I'll... join the
one who makes them come first♪
\n<Brown-haired man & Hat-wearing man>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F] 'We definitely won't lose!'

Kino is even going through unpleasant experiences
to help us. I know she's not a character, but it
would be disrespectful to her if we were to feel
embarrassed here.

Two pairs of men and women press their skin
together, burying their faces in each other's
crotches to comfort each other. In the midst of
that, I move to the blind spot of the men.

\n<Sawa>(...Thanks to Kino and the guys leading them well.
Wait a moment, I'll finish it quickly...)

I take out a small spray bottle that I had hidden
in the pocket of my jacket.

\n<Sawa>(I never thought that what Udo Director gave me
would actually be useful...)

...It was a suspicious sleep spray that was not
for sale. On the second night of the training
camp, I went to \N[5]-san's room and used it to
make him fall asleep.

First, I approach Kino and the others. The man
wearing a hat is completely absorbed in Kino's
crotch and doesn't notice my approach at all.

\n<Hat Man>Slurp, chu, chuba, fusu... fufu... Hm? Huh...?
Ahh... Zzz...

Kino stands up and heads towards Momo before I
even have a chance to stand up, gently supporting
the head of the man who has fallen asleep and
placing it on the floor.
\n<Sawa>...Kino?

\n<Brown-haired man>Haa, haa, Momo-chan\I[12] Momo-chan, I can't hold
back anymore...
\n<Kino>Hey, premature ejaculation guy.

\n<Brown-haired man>Huh? Kino-chan? What, you still long for my
dick... huh?!

Kino placed her foot on the face of the man she
looked up to...! Without hesitation, she stepped
on it with all her might.
\n<Brown-haired man>Ngoh... you, you...
\n<Momo>Mmmph!? Mm-mmph...

I hurriedly approached the man and sprayed his
face with a spray.

\n<Brown-haired man>Huh? Fuh... What's this... Nyannra... This... N...
Ah... Zzz...

\n<Kino>Heh... This guy came from having his head stepped
on and ejaculated.
\n<Sawa>Geez... You got a little flustered, didn't you...

\n<Kino>Sorry, sorry... but this guy's smug face is really
pissing me off...

\n<Momo>Cough, cough... Ugh... It's stuck in the back of
my throat...

The atmosphere suddenly changed and was filled
with relief.

\n<Sawa>\F[66] ...With this, he shouldn't wake up for a
few hours. Let's meet up with \N[5]-san and the
others.

\n<Momo>\F[66]\FF[92]\AA[FF] That went well, didn't it? He
was completely off guard.

\n<Sawa>That... might be thanks to Kino. If Udo-san had
received a confirmation call, it could have been
dangerous...

\n<Kino>\F[66]\FF[91]\AA[FF] For Sawa, that was just a
coincidence... What were you planning to do if
these guys tried to contact us?

\n<Sawa>\F[66]\FF[91]\AA[F] Well... at that time, I was
thinking of hugging him, maybe even taking off our
clothes and forcefully taking it to the next
level...

\n<Momo>\F[66]\FF[92]\AA[FF] My perspective on Sawa-chan
has changed after this incident...

\n<Kino>They say the quiet ones are the scariest. But
personally, I have a good impression of
\F[66]\FF[91]\AA[FF].

\n<Sawa>\F[66]\FF[91]\AA[F] I was just desperate... B-but
more importantly, put on some clothes! Once you
take their cell phones, hurry back!

And so... we successfully cut off the means of
communication to the town, leaving the sleeping
men behind and leaving the cabin behind...
